Trading 

Coins have texture depending on how much they are offered

Icon	Coins Required
	0 Coins
	1-99,999 Coins
	100,000-9,999,999 Coins
	10,000,000-99,999,999 Coins
	100,000,000+ Coins

  Icon is below
  0 coins isnt valid
  sends a
&cYou cannot scam with negative gold!


&cYou cancelled the trade!

&cMissing arguments! Usage: /trade <player name>

&cYou can't trade with yourself!

&cYou are too far away to trade with that player!

Target requires to be 30 blocks or closer or gets that message



&aYou have sent a trade request to %colorofname%xzcb_&a.

&cYour /trade request to %colorofnameandrank% xzcb_ &cexpired!

&cThe /trade request from &b[MVP&c+&b] Vicente_1313 &cexpired!


§bVicente_1313 §ahas sent you a trade request. §bClick here §ato accept!
on hover &6Click to trade!

Items and coins can be shared inside the trading menu, with 16 stacks of items (or 1,024,000,000 coins). However, only 50,000,000 coins can be traded per day below SkyBlock Level 50 , 1,000,000,000 coins above SkyBlock Level 50 , and 10,000,000,000 coins above SkyBlock Level 100 .
